<section class="help-card">
  <div class="help-card__eyebrow">Budgeting</div>
  <h2 class="help-card__title">What to budget for beyond rent</h2>

  <div class="help-card__grid help-card__grid--tight">
    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Base rent</h3>
      <p>
        The headline rate is just the starting point. Understand how rent escalates over time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Operating expenses</h3>
      <p>
        CAM, NNN, taxes, insurance, utilities, and janitorial can significantly impact total cost.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Upfront costs</h3>
      <p>
        Deposits, moving, furniture, internet setup, and possible improvements add up quickly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Flexibility tradeoffs</h3>
      <p>
        Shorter terms and turnkey spaces are easier, but often come at a higher effective rate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>